Command list
pext    : Get external pressure

date    : Get date
gps     : GPS synchronization
iridium : Iridium transfer
mstart  : Start mermaid acq
mstop   : Stop mermaid acq
mdata   : Get mermaid datas
ls      : List files
cat     : Print content of a file
rm      : Remove a file
h       : Print command list
q       : Quit
